I developed a custom lead generation campaign for a top UK law firm targeting the mis-sold car finance scandal. This included building a bespoke frontend form integrated with the DVLA API to auto-fill vehicle registration data. The system captured key claimant information—including signatures, IP addresses, lender agreements, and passport photos—streamlining the legal onboarding process. In just five months, we reached over 17,000 claimants, secured 7,000+ digital signatures, and collected 4,000 verified IDs.
